## 15. RISKS & MITIGATIONS

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| No pilots sign up | Lower to €497. Personal outreach to 20+. |
| Clients don't engage | System escalates after 3 days silence. Week 4 training call. |
| Claude API costs spike | Use Sonnet. Fall back to Ollama for non-critical. |
| Too many features, nothing ships | Phase 1 = EE only. Publish Engine parallel because it's for YOU. |
| Capacity crunch | Circuit breaker: >12 hrs/week for 3 weeks → stop new clients. |
| TikTok audit rejection | Start with Direct Post to drafts. Public posting after audit. |
| LinkedIn token expiry (60 days) | n8n reminder workflow. Move to Community Management API when business entity registered. |
| Ziplined dependency during migration | Run both parallel. Cut Ziplined after 4 weeks of stable Publish Engine. |

